// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DlVBzy latitudes and longitudes, 2023 by jt
// using https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DdX3z4 euclidean distance sdf debugger by jt

// SDF to visualize latitudes and longitudes.
// As far as I can tell this sdf is exact (but feel free to doublecheck).
// (I hope the flash at the start is just a false alarm due to hitting a sdf gradient discontinuity).

// tags: latitude, longitude, sdf, distance, euclidean, exact, debug, loopless

